<h1>Dragons!</h1>

<h2>Dragons embody the greatest virtues living beings can expose.  As well as the worst.</h2>

<ul>
  {{#each dragons}}
    {{#unless evil}}
      {{> dragons/dragon-block evil=1}}
    {{/unless}}
  {{/each}}
</ul>

<h2>Consumed by their power, dragons rampage.  Still, there is always hope.</h2>

<ul>
  {{#each dragons}}
    {{#if evil}}
      {{> dragons/dragon-block evil=0}}
    {{/if}}
  {{/each}}
</ul>

<h2>Add a Dragon</h2>
<form class="create-form">

  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="ca">Dragon Name:</label>
    <input type="text" id="ca" name="name">
  </div>

  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="sleepy">Evil?</label><br>
    <input type="radio" name="evil" value="1" checked> Evil!<br>
    <input type="radio" name="evil" value="0"> Reedemed!
  </div>

  <button type="submit">Add the Dragon!</button>
</form>
